<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note25" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref25
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">25</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/2.html#T342d
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">342<SPAN CLASS="small">D</SPAN></A>, <I>infra</I>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note26" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref26
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">26</A>
<I>Cf.</I> Müller, <I>Frag. Hist. Graec.</I> <SPAN CLASS="small">II</SPAN> p472.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note27" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref27
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">27</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <I>Life of Alexander</I>,
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Alexander*/3.html#8.2
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
chaps. <SPAN CLASS="smaller">VIII</SPAN> (p. 668<SPAN CLASS="small">D</SPAN>)
	</A>
and
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Alexander*/4.html#26
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
<SPAN CLASS="smaller">XXVI</SPAN> (679<SPAN CLASS="small">C-D</SPAN>)</A>;
	<A HREF="
