	"TARGET="princeps"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,1,WIDTH,165)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Diogenes Laertius, <SPAN CLASS="small">VI</SPAN>.81</A>), was said to have been a pupil of Chrysippus, and thus was converted to the inheritance of Zeno, Stoicism.


