<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>philosophy


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note52" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref52
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
