"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">54</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <I>Moralia</I>, 179<SPAN CLASS="small">D</SPAN>;
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Alexander*/3.html#4.10
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
<I>Life of Alexander</I>, chap. <SPAN CLASS="smaller">IV</SPAN> (666<SPAN CLASS="small">D</SPAN>)</A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note55" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref55
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">55</A>
Attributed to a Spartan woman in <I>Moralia</I>, 241<SPAN CLASS="small">E</SPAN>, where see the note.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note56" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref56
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">56</A>
<I>Iliad</I>, <SPAN CLASS="small">III</SPAN>.179; <I>cf.</I> Xenophon, <I>Memorabilia</I>, <SPAN CLASS="small">III</SPAN>.2.2.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note57" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref57
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">57</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Alexander*/3.html#visits_Troy
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();"><I>Life of Alexander</I>, chap. <SPAN CLASS="smaller">XV</SPAN> (672<SPAN CLASS="small">B</SPAN>)</A>; Aelian, <I>Varia Historia</I>, <SPAN CLASS="small">IX</SPAN>.38.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note58" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref58
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">58</A>
Homer, <I>Il.</I> <SPAN CLASS="small">IX</SPAN>.189.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note59" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref59
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">59</A>
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#T327f
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,5,WIDTH,140)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
327<SPAN CLASS="small">F</SPAN></A>, <I>supra</I>; <I>cf.</I> <A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Alexander*/3.html#T668a
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();"><I>Life of Alexander</I>, chaps. <SPAN CLASS="smaller">VII</SPAN>, <SPAN CLASS="smaller">VIII</SPAN> (668<SPAN CLASS="small">A-F</SPAN>)</A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note60" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref60
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">60</A>
<I>Cf.</I> Sextus Empiricus, <I>Adversus Mathematicos</I>, <SPAN CLASS="small">I</SPAN>.282.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note61" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref61
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
