<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note62" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref62
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">62</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <I>Life of Alexander</I>, chaps. <SPAN CLASS="smaller">LXV</SPAN>, <SPAN CLASS="smaller">LXVI</SPAN> (<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Alexander*/9.html#65
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
