702<SPAN CLASS="small">A</SPAN></A>); Arrian, <I>Anabasis</I>, <SPAN CLASS="small">VI</SPAN>.2.3, <SPAN CLASS="small">VII</SPAN>.5.6;
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Diogenes_Laertius/Lives_of_the_Eminent_Philosophers/6/Onesicritus*.html#84
	"TARGET="princeps"
