Valerius Maximus, <SPAN CLASS="small">IV</SPAN>.3.4</A>;
	<A HREF="
https://www.curculio.org/Juvenal/s14.html
	"TARGET="offsite"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(EClickHere+'Juvenal\'s 14th Satire'+Lat2+LatSearch+'sensit</SPAN>',WIDTH,195)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Juvenal, <SPAN CLASS="small">XIV</SPAN>.311‑314</A>. <I>Cf.</I> also <I>Moralia</I>, 782<SPAN CLASS="small">A-B</SPAN>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
