<I>Cf.</I> Arrian, <I>Anabasis</I>, <SPAN CLASS="small">IV</SPAN>.10.6; <I>Rhein. Mus.</I> <SPAN CLASS="small">LIV</SPAN>.470.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
