	</A>
for Alexander's dealings with the Gymnosophists.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note67" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref67
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">67</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Diogenes_Laertius/Lives_of_the_Eminent_Philosophers/6/Diogenes*.html#20
	"TARGET="princeps"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,1,WIDTH,165)"
onMouseOut="nd();">Diogenes Laertius, <SPAN CLASS="small">VI</SPAN>.20, 21</A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note68" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/1.html#ref68
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">68</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <I>Moralia</I>, 181<SPAN CLASS="small">E</SPAN>, and 458<SPAN CLASS="small">B</SPAN>;
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Alexander*/8.html#60.14
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
